   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give 2300 Colombian Children a Reason to Smile</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Benefits 2300 vulnerable kids traumatized by poverty and violence teaching them core values and life skills through sports in guided classes providing a healthy lifestyle and a physical and psychosocial development, using physical education, sports and recreation as a tool for social integration. This provides a better use of their free time thus keeping them off drugs and violence. We are instilling behavioral models that shape their future performance by providing them a better quality of life</narrative>
  </description>
